headline.print_headline: Roswell Is Golden Girl but Kenny Settles for Silver Again
headline.main: Roswell Is Golden Girl but Kenny Settles for Silver Again

lead_paragraph: Joanna Roswell added a first Commonwealth Games title to Olympic team gold with a dominant ride in the 3,000m individual pursuit on Friday but England colleague Jason Kenny had to settle for silver.
